supportDesc.extent: 304 leaves : 207 x 157 (174 x 114) mm. bound to 215 x 165 mm

collation.p: Paper, i (contemporary paper) + 304 + i (contemporary paper); 1⁶(first leaf flyleaf) 2-5⁸ 6² 7⁶ 8-29⁸ 30¹² 31⁸ 32¹⁰ 33-38⁸ 39⁸(-2, perhaps pastedown; last leaf flyleaf); [1-304]; modern foliation in pencil, upper right recto. Gatherings 1-23 signed A-Z (gathering 1 signed on second leaf; no J, U, or W), gathering 24 signed with a crossed Z, gatherings 25-39 signed AA-PP (no J).

scriptDesc.scriptNote: Written in a small cursive script by what appears to be a single hand, with marginal annotations in a similar hand.

history.provenance: Formerly in the library of the Carthusian monastery in Buxheim (inscriptions, f. i recto, 1r).
